:{{DIcon|Arrow}} This is too hard!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202010112-->
::'''Tantan:''' ...
::'''Tantan:''' Hearing you say that makes me feel a little better. You're not saying that just to console me, are you?
